            </b></br><img style="max-width: 100%;" src="{{ asset('uploads/custom/images/1626.png') }}" alt="1626.png"></li>
            <li>de <b>créer </b>de nombreuses ressources <img style="max-width: 100%;" src="{{ asset('uploads/custom/images/1631.png') }}"
